### MOVIX E2E Demo — REST Client (VS Code)
### Set variables: BASE_URL, ADMIN_TOKEN, TENANT_ID, PASSENGER_TOKEN, DRIVER_TOKEN, TRIP_ID, PAYMENT_ID

@BASE_URL = http://localhost:8080
@ADMIN_TOKEN = your_admin_token_here
@TENANT_ID = your_tenant_guid_here
@PASSENGER_TOKEN = your_passenger_token_here
@DRIVER_TOKEN = your_driver_token_here
@TRIP_ID = your_trip_guid_here
@PAYMENT_ID = your_payment_guid_here

### 0. Health
GET {{BASE_URL}}/health

### 1. Auth — Login Admin
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@movix.local",
  "password": "TuPasswordSeguro"
}

### 2. Auth — Register Passenger
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "passenger@demo.local",
  "password": "Pass1234"
}

### 3. Auth — Login Passenger
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "passenger@demo.local",
  "password": "Pass1234"
}

### 4. Admin — Create Tenant
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/admin/tenants
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Demo City"
}

### 5. Admin — Get Tenants
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/admin/tenants
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}

### 6. Admin — Create Tariff (requires X-Tenant-Id)
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/admin/tariffs
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{TENANT_ID}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Standard",
  "currency": "USD",
  "baseFare": 2.50,
  "pricePerKm": 1.20,
  "pricePerMinute": 0.25,
  "minimumFare": 5.00
}

### 7. Admin — Activate Tariff (replace {tariffId})
# POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/admin/tariffs/{tariffId}/activate
# Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}
# X-Tenant-Id: {{TENANT_ID}}

### 8. Fare — Quote (requires X-Tenant-Id)
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/fare/quote?distanceKm=5&durationMin=10
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{TENANT_ID}}

### 9. Driver — Onboarding
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/drivers/onboarding
Authorization: Bearer {{DRIVER_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "licenseNumber": "DL-001",
  "vehiclePlate": "ABC-123",
  "vehicleModel": "Sedan",
  "vehicleColor": "White"
}

### 10. Driver — Status Online (status: 0=Offline, 1=Online, 2=Busy, 3=OnTrip)
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/drivers/status
Authorization: Bearer {{DRIVER_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": 1
}

### 11. Trips — Create (Idempotency-Key + X-Tenant-Id required)
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/trips
Authorization: Bearer {{PASSENGER_TOKEN}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{TENANT_ID}}
Idempotency-Key: demo-trip-1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pickupLatitude": 9.0,
  "pickupLongitude": -79.5,
  "dropoffLatitude": 9.05,
  "dropoffLongitude": -79.55,
  "pickupAddress": "Origin",
  "dropoffAddress": "Dest",
  "estimatedAmount": 10.50,
  "currency": "USD"
}

### 12. Trips — Assign Driver
# POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/trips/{{TRIP_ID}}/assign-driver
# Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}
# X-Tenant-Id: {{TENANT_ID}}

### 13. Trips — Arrive
# POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/trips/{{TRIP_ID}}/arrive
# Authorization: Bearer {{DRIVER_TOKEN}}
# X-Tenant-Id: {{TENANT_ID}}

### 14. Trips — Start
# POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/trips/{{TRIP_ID}}/start
# Authorization: Bearer {{DRIVER_TOKEN}}
# X-Tenant-Id: {{TENANT_ID}}

### 15. Trips — Complete (fare snapshot: distanceKm, durationMinutes)
# POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/trips/{{TRIP_ID}}/complete
# Authorization: Bearer {{DRIVER_TOKEN}}
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# {
#   "distanceKm": 5.2,
#   "durationMinutes": 12,
#   "tenantId": null
# }

### 16. Trips — Get by Id
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/trips/{{TRIP_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{PASSENGER_TOKEN}}

### 17. Payments — Create (Idempotency-Key required)
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/payments
Authorization: Bearer {{PASSENGER_TOKEN}}
Idempotency-Key: demo-pay-1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tripId": "{{TRIP_ID}}",
  "amount": 10.50,
  "currency": "USD"
}

### 18. Payments — Simulate Webhook (Development only)
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/payments/simulate-webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentId": "{{PAYMENT_ID}}",
  "eventType": "payment_intent.succeeded"
}

### 19. Admin Ops — Get Payments (filter by status)
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/admin/ops/payments?status=Completed
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}

### 20. Admin Ops — Get Outbox (deadletters)
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/admin/ops/outbox?deadletter=true
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}

### 21. Admin Ops — Reprocess DeadLetter (replace {outboxId})
# POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/admin/ops/outbox/{outboxId}/reprocess
# Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}
